Awka Baboon: Ejidela enwe 'JohnBull' tara nwata akwụkwọ n'Awka, Anambra State
Ejidela utobo ya bụ enwe 'JohnBull' ahụ tara nwata akwụkwọ n'Awka, Anambra State.
Ndị nwe ụlọọgwụ 'Centre for Psychic Healing' dị n'Awka bụ Flora Ilonzo agwala BBC etu a.
Ebe foto si, Getty Images/BBC
Awka Baboon: Ejidela enwe 'JohnBull' tara nwata akwụkwọ n'Awka, Anambra State
Flora Ilonzo onye nwe ụlọọgwụ 'Centre for Psychic Healing' dị n'Awka dị n'Awka gwara BBC na ọ bụ ụdị enwe bụ utobo, o dosara n'ụlọ anụmanụ gbapụrụ, na ọ bụghị ozodimgba dịka ndị mmadụ siri akọ.
Ilonzo kwuru na ọ zụtara enwe a kamgbe afọ iri na abụọ gara aga dịka otu n'ime ọtụtụ anụmanụ o ji mere ihe nkiri n'ụlọọgwụ ya.
Ihe ụmụ anụmanụ pụtara n'akụkọ ifo Igbo
Anụmanụ atọ ndị ga-abara gị uru n'ụzọ ị tụghị anya
Enyi mmiri atagbuola mmadụ na Kenya
Mgbe BBC rutere n'ogige ahụ, a hụrụ ọtụtụ anụmanụ ndị ọzọ mana enwe a tara mmadụ alaghachibeghị n'ụlọ nchekwa e dosara ya.
Ilonzo gwara BBC Igbo na ọ bụ na Tuzdee ka enwe ahụ a kpọrọ Johnbull richara nrị wee pụọ n'ebe e dosara ya.
Flora Ilonzo bụ onye nwe ụlọọgwụ 'Centre for Psychic Healing' dị n'Awka.
Mgbe ọ pụrụ ezi ka ụmụakwụkwọ malitere ịma ya okwute nke mere o ji taa otu nwata akwụkwọ.
Flora Ilonzo kwuru na ọ bụ ya zụtara ọgwụ 'anti-rabbies' nke a gbara nwata akwụkwọ ahụ.
Ndị uweojii mekwara nchọpụta hụ na ya bụ nwatakịrị alaghachila n'ụlọakwụkwọ kamgbe a gbachara ya ọgwụ ahụ.
Enwe ahụ bụ Johnbull ka nọkwa n'ime ọhịa gburugburu ụlọọgwụ ahụ
Utobu na-awakpo ndị mmadụ n'Ọka, Anambra Steeti
Ebe foto si, Getty Images
Awka Baboon: Ejidela enwe 'JohnBull' tara nwata akwụkwọ n'Awka, Anambra State
Utobo si ebe edowere ya agbapụ na-enye ndị bị na mpaghara Commissioners Quaters nke dị n'Ọka, Anambra steeti nsogbu

Otu onye ji akara @Zomsy na Twitter dere na utobo si  n'ụlọ ọgwụgwọ akpọrọ "Centre for Psychic Healing Awka"  gbapụ ma na-enye nsogbu na mpaghara obi gọọmenti dị n'Ọka, Anambra steeti. Na nkọwa nwa amadị a, utobo a na-agbapụ aga gburugburu  ụka St. Thomas Acquinas na ụzọ Commissioner's Quarters were na-awakpo ma na emerụ ndị mmadụ ezigbote ahụ.
'E si na mba Kamerun wee zubata ọdụm a hụrụ n'ụlọ anyị'- Onye nche
Lee 'ụmụanụmanụ' ga-achịpụ ya n'asọmpi AFCON 2019
O kwuru na mwakpo utobo a emerụọla ụmụaka na-aga akwụkwọ ahụ site na mwakpo ya.Awka Baboon: Ejidela enwe 'JohnBull' tara nwata akwụkwọ n'Awka, Anambra State
Foto nwa amadị a tinyere n'akara Twitter ya gosiri mmerụ ahụ ụfọdụ ọ si adaka a merụrụ ndị mmadụ.
Awka Baboon: Ejidela enwe 'JohnBull' tara nwata akwụkwọ n'Awka, Anambra State
Ọ na-arịọ gọọmenti ka ọ gbatara ndị mmadụ enyemaka maka ihe a.
Ọka bụ obodo eji nsọ enwe mara, mana adaka adịghị ka ọ bụ nke akpa ala ya si Ọka.

Enyi Nnụnụ
